      <h2>First section heading</h2>

      <p>Body copy goes here. Write the same way you'd explain it to a founder over coffee. Plain language, no jargon. If you need to use a legal term, define it immediately after.</p>

      <p>Keep paragraphs short. Two to four sentences maximum. White space is your friend.</p>

      <h2>Second section heading</h2>

      <p>Continue the article here.</p>

